query: What is the highest balance for an account that was created this week?

query: What is the sum of all transaction amounts that are whole numbers (no cents)?
sql_command: SELECT SUM(transaction_amount) FROM Transactions WHERE transaction_amount = FLOOR(transaction_amount);

query: How many cards have a balance of exactly $500?
sql_command: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Cards WHERE balance = 500;

query: What is the average interest rate for loans with a payment term of 360 months?
sql_command: SELECT AVG(interest_rate) FROM Loans WHERE payment_term = 360;

query: How many deposit types include the word 'Premium' in their description?
sql_command: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM DepositTypes WHERE description LIKE '%Premium%';

query: How many customers have an address located on a 'Road'?
sql_command: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Customers WHERE address LIKE '% Road';

query: How many accounts have an account number starting with 'ACC'?
sql_command: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Accounts WHERE account_number LIKE 'ACC%';

query: What is the total number of transactions made on the 1st of any month?
sql_command: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Transactions WHERE EXTRACT(DAY FROM transaction_date) = 1;

query: What is the total balance on cards that expire next month?
sql_command: SELECT SUM(balance) FROM Cards WHERE DATE_TRUNC('month', expiration_date) = DATE_TRUNC('month', CURRENT_DATE + INTERVAL '1 month');

query: How many loans have a balance greater than zero but less than $1000?
sql_command: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Loans WHERE balance > 0 AND balance < 1000;

query: What is the total balance of all deposits with a term longer than 5 years (60 months)?
sql_command: SELECT SUM(balance) FROM Deposits WHERE term > 60;

query: How many customers have an email address with the '.net' top-level domain?
sql_command: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Customers WHERE email LIKE '%.net';

query: What is the lowest balance for an account created before the year 2020?
sql_command: SELECT MIN(account_balance) FROM Accounts WHERE created_at < '2020-01-01';

query: How many transactions were made in the second quarter (Q2) of 2025?
sql_command: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Transactions WHERE EXTRACT(QUARTER FROM transaction_date) = 2 AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM transaction_date) = 2025;

query: How many blocked cards have a zero balance?
sql_command: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Cards WHERE is_blocked = TRUE AND balance = 0;

query: What is the shortest payment term for a loan with an interest rate above 6%?
sql_command: SELECT MIN(payment_term) FROM Loans WHERE interest_rate > 6;

query: How many deposits have an interest rate that is not a whole number?
sql_command: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Deposits WHERE interest_rate != FLOOR(interest_rate);

query: How many branches have a branch code that ends with '1'?
sql_command: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Branches WHERE branch_code LIKE '%1';

query: What is the total number of customer records created on a Sunday?
sql_command: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Customers WHERE EXTRACT(ISODOW FROM created_at) = 7;

query: How many accounts have a balance that is an odd number?
sql_command: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Accounts WHERE account_balance % 2 != 0;

query: What is the largest withdrawal (most negative transaction) recorded?
sql_command: SELECT MIN(transaction_amount) FROM Transactions;

query: How many active cards expire on the 15th of any month?
sql_command: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Cards WHERE is_blocked = FALSE AND EXTRACT(DAY FROM expiration_date) = 15;

query: How many loans were started and ended in the same calendar year?
sql_command: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Loans WHERE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM start_date) = EXTRACT(YEAR FROM end_date);

query: What is the average balance of deposits started in the last 30 days?
sql_command: SELECT AVG(balance) FROM Deposits WHERE start_date >= CURRENT_DATE - INTERVAL '30 days';

query: How many customers have a middle initial in their name?
sql_command: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Customers WHERE customer_name LIKE '_% _% %_';

query: What is the sum of balances for accounts that have never been updated?
sql_command: SELECT SUM(account_balance) FROM Accounts WHERE created_at = updated_at;

query: How many transactions occurred between 8 AM and 9 AM?
sql_command: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Transactions WHERE EXTRACT(HOUR FROM transaction_date) = 8;

query: What is the total balance on cards that were issued before 2022?
sql_command: SELECT SUM(balance) FROM Cards WHERE created_at < '2022-01-01';

query: What is the maximum loan balance for loans starting in Q1 of this year?
sql_command: SELECT MAX(balance) FROM Loans WHERE EXTRACT(QUARTER FROM start_date) = 1 AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM start_date) = EXTRACT(YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE);

query: How many deposits have a term that is a prime number (e.g., 11, 13, 17, 19, 23)?
sql_command: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Deposits WHERE term IN (11, 13, 17, 19, 23);

query: How many customers have a customer name longer than 20 characters?
sql_command: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Customers WHERE LENGTH(customer_name) > 20;

query: How many accounts have a negative balance below -$1000?
sql_command: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Accounts WHERE account_balance < -1000;

query: What is the average transaction amount for transactions made on weekdays?
sql_command: SELECT AVG(transaction_amount) FROM Transactions WHERE EXTRACT(ISODOW FROM transaction_date) BETWEEN 1 AND 5;

query: How many cards expire in Q3 of any year?
sql_command: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Cards WHERE EXTRACT(QUARTER FROM expiration_date) = 3;

query: How many loans have an interest rate that is a multiple of 0.5?
sql_command: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Loans WHERE (interest_rate * 2) = FLOOR(interest_rate * 2);

query: What is the total number of deposits that will mature after 2030?
sql_command: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Deposits WHERE end_date > '2030-12-31';

query: How many loan types have a description shorter than 15 characters?
sql_command: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM LoanTypes WHERE LENGTH(description) < 15;

query: How many customers were born in the summer (June, July, August)?
sql_command: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Customers WHERE EXTRACT(MONTH FROM date_of_birth) IN (6, 7, 8);

query: What is the total balance of accounts with an ID number greater than 10000?
sql_command: SELECT SUM(account_balance) FROM Accounts WHERE account_id > 10000;

query: How many transactions were for exactly $1?
sql_command: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Transactions WHERE transaction_amount = 1;

query: What is the total balance of all blocked cards?
sql_command: SELECT SUM(balance) FROM Cards WHERE is_blocked = TRUE;

query: How many loans end on a weekend?
sql_command: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Loans WHERE EXTRACT(ISODOW FROM end_date) IN (6, 7);

query: What is the average interest rate for deposits with a balance over $100,000?
sql_command: SELECT AVG(interest_rate) FROM Deposits WHERE balance > 100000;

query: How many customers have a hyphen in their name?
sql_command: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Customers WHERE customer_name LIKE '%-%';

query: How many accounts have a balance with cents (not a whole dollar amount)?
sql_command: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Accounts WHERE account_balance != FLOOR(account_balance);

query: How many transactions were made in the last 10 minutes?
sql_command: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Transactions WHERE transaction_date >= NOW() - INTERVAL '10 minutes';

query: What is the number of cards that were created on a holiday (e.g., Dec 25th)?
sql_command: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Cards WHERE EXTRACT(MONTH FROM created_at) = 12 AND EXTRACT(DAY FROM created_at) = 25;

query: What is the total balance of loans that have been fully paid off?
sql_command: SELECT SUM(balance) FROM Loans WHERE balance = 0;

query: How many deposits have a term of 48 months?
sql_command: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Deposits WHERE term = 48;

query: How many branches have 'West' in their address?
sql_command: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Branches WHERE branch_address LIKE '%West%';

query: How many customers have a registered phone number that starts with '555'?
sql_command: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Customers WHERE phone LIKE '555%';

query: What is the maximum balance of an account created in the 1990s?
sql_command: SELECT MAX(account_balance) FROM Accounts WHERE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM created_at) BETWEEN 1990 AND 1999;

query: How many transactions were recorded on the 31st of any month?
sql_command: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Transactions WHERE EXTRACT(DAY FROM transaction_date) = 31;

query: How many cards have an odd-numbered card ID?
sql_command: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Cards WHERE card_id % 2 != 0;

query: What is the average loan term for loans with a balance below $10,000?
sql_command: SELECT AVG(payment_term) FROM Loans WHERE balance < 10000;

query: How many deposits were started on a Monday?
sql_command: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Deposits WHERE EXTRACT(ISODOW FROM start_date) = 1;

query: How many customers have a date of birth in the 21st century?
sql_command: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Customers WHERE date_of_birth >= '2001-01-01';

query: How many accounts have a balance that is perfectly divisible by 100?
sql_command: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Accounts WHERE account_balance % 100 = 0;

query: What is the total sum of withdrawals (negative transactions) made this year?
sql_command: SELECT SUM(transaction_amount) FROM Transactions WHERE transaction_amount < 0 AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM transaction_date) = EXTRACT(YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE);

query: How many cards expire on the first day of a month?
sql_command: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Cards WHERE EXTRACT(DAY FROM expiration_date) = 1;

query: What is the minimum interest rate on a loan?
sql_command: SELECT MIN(interest_rate) FROM Loans;

query: What is the total number of deposits with a 24-month term?
sql_command: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Deposits WHERE term = 24;

query: How many deposit types have 'Student' in their name?
sql_command: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM DepositTypes WHERE type LIKE '%Student%';

query: How many customers have a zip code '90210' in their address?
sql_command: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Customers WHERE address LIKE '%90210%';

query: What is the average balance of accounts updated in the last 24 hours?
sql_command: SELECT AVG(account_balance) FROM Accounts WHERE updated_at >= NOW() - INTERVAL '24 hours';

query: How many transactions were made for an amount between $99 and $100?
sql_command: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Transactions WHERE transaction_amount BETWEEN 99 AND 100;

query: What is the total number of blocked cards expiring this year?
sql_command: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Cards WHERE is_blocked = TRUE AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM expiration_date) = EXTRACT(YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE);

query: How many loans have a payment term that is not a multiple of 12?
sql_command: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Loans WHERE payment_term % 12 != 0;

query: What is the total balance of deposits with an interest rate of 2.5% or higher?
sql_command: SELECT SUM(balance) FROM Deposits WHERE interest_rate >= 2.5;

query: How many customers have the letter 'X' in their name?
sql_command: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Customers WHERE customer_name LIKE '%X%' OR customer_name LIKE '%x%';

query: How many accounts were created in Q4 of 2023?
sql_command: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Accounts WHERE created_at >= '2023-10-01' AND created_at < '2024-01-01';

query: What is the highest transaction amount recorded on a weekend?
sql_command: SELECT MAX(transaction_amount) FROM Transactions WHERE EXTRACT(ISODOW FROM transaction_date) IN (6, 7);

query: How many cards have a card number ending in '00'?
sql_command: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Cards WHERE card_number LIKE '%00';

query: What is the total outstanding balance for loans with a term of 5 years?
sql_command: SELECT SUM(balance) FROM Loans WHERE payment_term = 60;

query: How many deposits mature on a Friday?
sql_command: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Deposits WHERE EXTRACT(ISODOW FROM end_date) = 5;

query: How many customers have a phone number but no email?
sql_command: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Customers WHERE phone IS NOT NULL AND email IS NULL;

query: What is the sum of balances for accounts with a single-digit ID?
sql_command: SELECT SUM(account_balance) FROM Accounts WHERE account_id < 10;

query: How many transactions were made in the last 365 days?
sql_command: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Transactions WHERE transaction_date >= CURRENT_DATE - INTERVAL '365 days';

query: What is the number of unblocked cards that expire in Q1 of next year?
sql_command: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Cards WHERE is_blocked = FALSE AND EXTRACT(QUARTER FROM expiration_date) = 1 AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM expiration_date) = EXTRACT(YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE) + 1;

query: What is the average balance of loans that are already past their end date?
sql_command: SELECT AVG(balance) FROM Loans WHERE end_date < CURRENT_DATE;

query: How many deposits have a balance that is a multiple of 5000?
sql_command: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Deposits WHERE balance % 5000 = 0;

query: How many loan types have 'Home' in their type name?
sql_command: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM LoanTypes WHERE type LIKE '%Home%';

query: How many customers were born on Halloween (October 31st)?
sql_command: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Customers WHERE EXTRACT(MONTH FROM date_of_birth) = 10 AND EXTRACT(DAY FROM date_of_birth) = 31;

query: How many accounts have a balance of less than $1?
sql_command: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Accounts WHERE account_balance < 1 AND account_balance > 0;

query: What is the total number of transactions with negative amounts (withdrawals)?
sql_command: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Transactions WHERE transaction_amount < 0;

query: How many cards have been issued to customers in branch ID 7?
sql_command: SELECT COUNT(ca.card_id) FROM Cards ca JOIN Customers c ON ca.customer_id = c.customer_id WHERE c.branch_id = 7;

query: How many customers are registered in the bank who were born before the year 2000?
sql_command: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Customers WHERE date_of_birth < '2000-01-01';
